title: Parkes to be showcased in Australia's Capital City (Parkes Shire Council)
text: ( Source : Parkes Shire Council ) The Parkes region will be showcased at the 2015 Canberra Home Show this coming weekend 23-25 October. This major consumer event will be held at Canberra's Exhibition Park with an audience of over 23, 000
